{"tid":2449070,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"加拿大國會議員聯署去信移民部長要求為香港人完善「救生艇計劃」","createTime":"2021-03-16T11:22:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-19T05:05:34.000Z","uid":70063,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"01ad98d7382a39907f7aeda925ba748462ca3048","tid":2449070,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:22:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hk_watch/status/1371490596750245897?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhk_watch%2Fstatus%2F1371490596750245897%3Fs%3D19&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixWVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=95c409d4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhk_watch%2Fstatus%2F1371490596750245897%3Fs%3D19&h=47b80026\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hk_watch/status/1371490596750245897?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hk_watch/status/1371490598595796994?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhk_watch%2Fstatus%2F1371490598595796994%3Fs%3D19&d=JW7tglSI9GVP0ZLjrScixWVlCuV5KOpEhASsqV1EMe4%3D&h=716bce39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhk_watch%2Fstatus%2F1371490598595796994%3Fs%3D19&h=521ed0cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hk_watch/status/1371490598595796994?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n早前47名民主派人士因參與初選被政府以《港版國安法》控告「顛覆國家政權」。有見及此，加拿大十二位跨黨派國會議員聯署去信移民部長 Marco Mendicino 敦促加國政府為香港人完善早前推出的「救生艇計劃」，確保高風險的抗爭者能夠在當地尋得避風港。<br />\n<br />\n信中提出幾項建議，包括：<br />\n<br />\n（一）允許香港人於香港境外的加拿大領事館申請庇護；<br />\n<br />\n（二）允許獲得加拿大公民贊助、身處第三國家的香港人入境加國申請難民資格；<br />\n<br />\n（三）確保遭受政治迫害，被以「暴動」及「非法集會」等罪名起訴的抗爭者不會因此被取消庇護申請資格；<br />\n<br />\n（四）參考加國 Rainbow Refugee Assistance Pilot 計劃，為高風險抗爭者設立相應支援計劃；<br />\n<br />\n（五）延長現有 Youth Mobility International Experience Canada Program 至兩年，並將年齡限制擴大至 18-35 歲；<br />\n<br />\n（六）考慮運用於2002年通過的《移民和難民保護法》所賦予的立法權力，在必要時由移民部長發佈指令彌補漏洞。<br />\n<br />\n香港監察總監羅傑斯指：「是次聯署顯示了加國國會議員因47為民主派人士被捕而對香港人權狀況逐漸變壞愈加憂慮。我們希望加拿大政府可聽取各議員意見，完善相關計劃並為抗爭者提供逃生門。」"},{"pid":"50e4c2884742a8d762fb8355677420f5e3dcf120","tid":2449070,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:48:25.000Z","msg":"Good"},{"pid":"0b635c6a4a8bb2aa693620c32b3a2971b26e0446","tid":2449070,"uid":98431,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-16T11:50:55.000Z","msg":"唔望太多 淨係望條hk path可以救埋後生但未必有太多錢既手足"},{"pid":"0a7e86b7eb53b8dd7e96bbb25c8e074b89702e72","tid":2449070,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T01:24:49.000Z","msg":"多謝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b30dbf4c189956830283dd3fa19e7633a87b4c","tid":2449070,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T01:25:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5574ebd0103c0cb26fdce8ea04aba38f8b189783","tid":2449070,"uid":253016,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T01:27:12.000Z","msg":"都係個句<br />\n香港護照任支那印 點分香港人出黎先係重點<br />\n如果唔係最後都係支那豬天堂"},{"pid":"5dc6149e45116877e3610160014b6d77bc3f1fbc","tid":2449070,"uid":327169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T01:30:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f14b04e8a5ba8bfaeecc413ef7bdb74908ef3c5","tid":2449070,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T10:26:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/SenatorMunson/status/13718606943